:::The Keepers:::

::They wake up from there long stasis lock.  Suddenly, Datastreak feels 
something deep within his spark::
Datastreak: Herald, im feeling something.  Something from the Matrix.
HeraldAngel: I feel it too Data, and it seems to be coming from Arcangel.
::he turns to his son, Child, who is now the leader of his group::
HeraldAngel: Child, what should we do?
Child: I think we should find out what he is doing.
::Herald opens up a comm::
HeraldAngel: Arcangel, this is Herald.  were detecting something from the 
matrix, coming from you.  Whats going on?
